{"lemma":"جِماعٌ","slug":"جِماعٌ","root":"ج.م.ع","root_slug":"ج-م-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6317","n6321","n6322"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%90%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَامَعَ (jāmaʕa) (form III)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sexual intercourse, copulation, coitus"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6317","headword_ar":"جِمَاعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as signifying “ a plural, ” in three places. [The primary signification seems to be the last there mentioned; where it is said,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljimaAEu","text_ar":"الجِمَاعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What comprises a number"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of things]: (S, K:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxamoru jimaAEu AlA_ivomi","text_ar":"الخَمْرُ جِمَاعُ الاـِثْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wine is what comprises a number of sins:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that in which sin is comprised, and known to be:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the saying is a trad.: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAEu AlA_ivomi","text_ar":"جِمَاعُ الاـِثْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the plurality"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoE","text_ar":"جَمْع"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sins."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) Hence also the saying of El-Hasan El-Basree,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~aquwA h`*ihi","text_ar":"اِتَّقُوا هٰذِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ahowaA='a faA_in~a jimaAEahaA AlD~alaAlapu wamaEaAdahaA Aln~aAru","text_ar":"الاَهْوَا=ءَ فَاـِنَّ جِمَاعَهَا الضَّلَالَةُ وَمَعَادَهَا النَّارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Beware ye of these natural desires; for what they involve is error, and the place to which they lead is the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Hell]. (TA: in the L,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wmyEAdhA","text_ar":"وميعادها"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Had~ivoniY bikalimapK takuwnu jimaAEFA","text_ar":"حَدِّثْنِى بِكَلِمَةٍ تَكُونُ جِمَاعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Tell me a saying comprising"},{"kind":"text","text":"[virtually]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a plurality of sayings."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See a similar phrase below, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAmiEN","text_ar":"جَامِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buromapN jimaAEN","text_ar":"بُرْمَةٌ جِمَاعٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stonecooking-pot of the largest size:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, L:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qidorN","text_ar":"قِدْرٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAEN","text_ar":"جِمَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAmiEapN","text_ar":"جَامِعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cooking-pot that comprises a slaughtered camel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A, that comprises a sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great cooking-pot;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAmiEN","text_ar":"جَامِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Sgh, K:) pl. [most probably of this last]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumoEN","text_ar":"جُمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buzolN","text_ar":"بُزْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAzilN","text_ar":"بَازِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.]. (K.) ―         -b3-  You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN jimaAEN libaniY fulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ جِمَاعٌ لِبَنِى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is an object of resort for his counsel and authority to the sons of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  [See also 3.]"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Ks","L","Sgh"]},{"entry_id":"n6321","headword_ar":"جَمَّاعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mijomaEN","text_ar":"مِجْمَعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[are mentioned together, but not explained, in the TA: the former signifies, and probably, judging from analogy, the latter likewise, as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamuwEN","text_ar":"جَمُوعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who collects much;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who collects many things"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibilN jam~aAEapN","text_ar":"اـِبِلٌ جَمَّاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiyEN","text_ar":"جَمِيعٌ"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6322","headword_ar":"جُمَّاعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Anything of which the several component parts are collected, brought, gathered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawn, together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] as an epithet, applied to a woman, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Short."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aAEN Alv~uray~aA","text_ar":"جُمَّاعٌ الثُّرَيَّا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The cluster of the Pleiades:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persons who collect together for the rain of the Pleiades, which is the rain called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlwasomiY~","text_ar":"الوَسْمِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"looking for the fruitfulness and herbage resulting from it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aAEu","text_ar":"جُمَّاعُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A medley,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"promiscuous multitude"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collection, of men,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of various tribes;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aAEN","text_ar":"جُمَّاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone: (TA:) or the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"people scattered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of dispersion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 302.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aAEN","text_ar":"جُمَّاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place"},{"kind":"text","text":"[either properly or tropically]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which comprises the origin"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything; (K, TA;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"source of descent"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extraction"},{"kind":"text","text":"of people; and hence applied by I 'Ab to main tribes from which other tribes are derived; or, as some say, used by him as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"various classes of men, such as are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awozaAE","text_ar":"اَوْزَاع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awo$aAb","text_ar":"اَوْشَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b6-  [And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most essential, part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing. Thus,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aAEu jasadi AlA_inosaAni","text_ar":"جُمَّاعُ جَسَدِ الاـِنْسَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The head of the man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aAEu Alt~amori","text_ar":"جُمَّاعُ التَّمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The contraction"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajam~uE","text_ar":"تَجَمُّع"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the envelopes of the flowers of dates, in one place, upon"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the germs of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fruit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produce, thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["IDrd","S","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%AC%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B9/","headword_ar":"جماعة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_15","lexicon_en":"Ibn Mālik, al-Alfāẓ al-Mukhtalifa fī l-Maʿānī al-Muʾtalifa (d. 1274 CE)","lexicon_ar":"الألفاظ المختلفة في المعاني المؤتلفة لابن مالك","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=22424#f74349","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">بَاب الْجَمَاعَة</span><br><br><span>حزب وَطَائِفَة وَفرْقَة وعصبة ورهط وفئام وأحزاب وكردوس وفوج وثلة وَجَمَاعَة وملأ وزمر وكتيبة وفيلق وَنَفر وزرافات وخميس وجيش وشرذمة </span>"}]}}